data.description:
<<<MOTIVATED SELLER>>>Beautiful Home at 1804 Castle Creek Drive, Little Elm, TX 75068! This 4 bed, 3 bath, 2-story gem offers 3,153 sqft of comfortable living space on a spacious corner lot.

Step into the welcoming open entry flooded with natural light, setting the tone for a delightful living experience. The large master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom and a generously sized walk-in closet.

Three additional bedrooms provide ample space for a growing family or guests. All three bathrooms are tastefully designed with modern fixtures.

This property includes a fully fenced yard on a corner lot, perfect for outdoor activities and entertaining. Located in desirable Little Elm, this home is close to amenities, schools, parks, and more.

Sellers have an assumable mortgage and interest rate of 2.87% with a qualifying FHA loan! Don't miss your chance to make 1804 Castle Creek Drive your forever home. Schedule a viewing today!
